<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>A <db:link xlink:href="qt3drender-qclearbuffers.xml">Qt3DRender::QClearBuffers</db:link> FrameGraph node enables clearing of the specific render target buffers with specific values.</db:para>
